        <changelog><![CDATA[Initial ReaPack release.
- Shared engine (ArticulationRoll_lib.lua) ported 1:1 from the Ableton extension.
- Pop-up menu action (assign / clear / rebuild / edit map).
- 8 bindable per-slot assign actions + Clear + Rebuild, all in the MIDI Editor section.]]></changelog>

