      <metadata>
        <description><![CDATA[Articulation Roll for REAPER

Tag melodic notes with an articulation and auto-generate the matching keyswitch
notes into the take — the Reaticulate-style workflow, ported 1:1 from the Ableton
"Articulation Roll" extension.

Install registers a pop-up menu plus bindable per-slot assign actions (1-8),
Clear, and Rebuild in the MIDI Editor action list. Edit the articulation map at
<REAPER resource path>/ArticulationRoll_map.txt.]]></description>
        <link rel="website">https://github.com/AviouslyAvi/ableton-extensions/tree/main/02-extensions/articulation-roll/reaper</link>
